[{'action': 'opened', 'author': 'marcoemrich', 'comment_id': None, 'datetime': '2018-03-27 20:08:18+00:00', 'masked_author': 'username_0', 'text': "## Why Snacks?

The night before was a party. If the attendees don't need a snack now, they must have some other secret sauce to get their bodies back up to speed. But many rely on a sponsor to help out and prevent a low blood sugar by providing quick energy refilling snacks in the form of sweets, baked goods and candy. Keep those hard working brains happy - either by choosing yourself what to get or just leave it up to us to find the right sugar-bombs!

## How does it work?

Last year we asked some food companies for offers and had the sponsor confirm that amount up front. Once the food was delivered on the day the sponsor pulled out the credit card and made all attendees happy by enabling them to making the blood sugar level catch up.", 'title': 'Sponsor needed for snacks on Saturday', 'type': 'issue'}
